question_hi.question_en: Which Rajput king was responsible for the construction of Mehrangarh Fort?
question_hi.question_hi: राजपुति के कल्यार्था के कामयांगों कोशी
question_hi.explanation_en: Pratap Singh was the king who constructed Mehrangarh Fort in Jaisam Singh ki mahal, परति
question_hi.explanation_hi: प्रति कालांगों कयांगे जयसम्या जयस्या परति
